data.description: Check out this 4 bedroom, 2 bath home on over an acre of land! The kitchen in this home will throughly impress you! It includes a large island with ample room for bar seating, perfect for breakfasts or a quick meal.  It also has a large farmhouse sink, a combination of pendant and recessed lighting, and plenty of cabinets, and an open concept with the living room.  Apart from the room for dining in the kitchen, there is also a separate flex space as you enter the home that could be used as a dining room or whatever suits your lifestyle.  The owner's suite features double vanities, a garden tub perfect for unwinding after a day at work, and a separate shower.  With. the three additional bedrooms and second full bathroom, this home is ready for a family to make it theirs!
